of Adam and Eve.

00:36:07.410 --> 00:36:09.100
I mean, think about that.

00:36:09.100 --> 00:36:12.450
Now, as artists Saint John's
comes to you and says,

00:36:12.450 --> 00:36:14.400
"Guess what, we've chosen Creation.

00:36:14.400 --> 00:36:17.070
We want you to make a brand
new image of the Creation.

00:36:17.070 --> 00:36:19.040
We want you to make it literal
so people know it's Creation,

00:36:19.040 --> 00:36:22.340
but we also want you to weave in
modern science and modern values.

00:36:22.340 --> 00:36:24.540
We want to make sure
that in 500 years

00:36:24.540 --> 00:36:25.840
from now people will
know it's Creation,

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:30.220
so make sure it's prophetic, and
don't make anybody mad, okay?

00:36:31.490 --> 00:36:36.060
[Laughter] And also it's a
Bible so you're going to deal

00:36:36.060 --> 00:36:37.620
