00:36:37.620 --> 00:36:39.930
And if we're making pictures,

00:36:39.930 --> 00:36:42.150
you might as well get
this over with right away.

00:36:42.150 --> 00:36:45.230
Figure out how you're
going to image God.

00:36:45.230 --> 00:36:48.970
I mean, think about just
that one assignment.

00:36:48.970 --> 00:36:52.240
How do you make an image of the
Divine and not make somebody mad?

00:36:52.240 --> 00:36:56.630
Well, that's exactly what
we asked the artist to do.

00:36:56.630 --> 00:37:01.050
So what I'd like you to do now is
I'm going to show you that artwork.

00:37:01.050 --> 00:37:02.880
And I want you to sit in silence,

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:06.030
for about 30 seconds,
and just look at it.

00:37:06.030 --> 00:37:09.280
And ask yourself, "What do I see?"

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:10.680
Don't talk to your
neighbor, just look at it.

00:37:10.680 --> 00:37:12.510
This is Creation.

00:37:12.510 --> 00:37:33.290
[ Background Sounds ]

00:37:33.290 --> 00:37:35.430
Now, turn to the person next
to you and just talk about it.

00:37:35.430 --> 00:37:37.510
Tell them what you see.

00:37:37.510 --> 00:38:36.940
